// Returns a 45 degree angle coordinate associated with the two given 
// coordinates
// 
// Parameters:
// x1 - First coordinate's x value
// x2 - Second coordinate's x value
// y1 - First coordinate's y value
// y2 - Second coordinate's y value
//
